final_hyps.green: The green object is the Goal that the agent must reach.
final_hyps.brown: Brown objects are False Walls. The agent can move through False Walls.
final_hyps.yellow: The yellow object is a Key. The agent can pick up the Key by moving into its space. While holding the Key, the agent is colored purple.
final_hyps.cyan: The cyan object is a KeyDoor. When the agent moves onto this object, the KeyDoor opens and the Key is destroyed. The agent cannot move through the KeyDoor while it is closed.

solve_plan: First determine that the green object is the Goal object. Move to pick up the yellow Key at (13, 8) by moving RIGHT. Because the agent is at x=5, it must move RIGHT 13 - 5 = 8 times. Next, align the agent on the vertical axis (y=10) by moving UP. Because the agent is at y=8, it must move UP 10 - 8 = 2 times. Then, move to reach the cyan KeyDoor at (18, 8) by moving RIGHT. The agent will open the KeyDoor and destroy the Key. Next, move the agent to reach the goal (x=19) by moving RIGHT. Because the agent is at x=18, it must move RIGHT 19 - 18 = 1 time.
